    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2238310/extras/60ff399f4146c506da690ad90ec27e28.avif?t=1707233583\" width=700 height=422 /></span> <br>Come Cook With Us<br><br>Welcome to the Dupont Family. A nice, quiet household in the Nova Scotia, Canada. Let's learn together how to cook delicious meals for you and your family. Because remember, can't live with an empty belly!<br>Find the VHS scattered around the house through a random system of placement in order to find the code to escape the house.<br>The first of a scheduled trilogy of games involving the Dupont Family, The Cooking Class is an homage to VHS found footage horror, 80's and 90's slasher movies, and the story of a family and its legacy and connections.<br>A first person atmospheric game, where the players will have to find their way out.<br><br>There are many hidden subplots and side stories that will be revealed through alternate channels and game sequels. There is an alive, vibrant world behind The Cooking Class, with a featured Youtube Channel, an Instagram page and much more to come.",
